Package: SimpLin
Type: Package
Title: Fit a Simple Linear Regression Model for Numeric Predictor and Response Variable
Version: 1.0
Date: 2024-01-29
Author: Hyungjoon Kim
Maintainer: Hyungjoon Kim <Hyungjoon.Kim@colostate.edu>
Description: A package to fit a simple linear regression model for a data 
    consists of one numeric predictor variable and a numeric response variable.
    It gives a vector of estimated regression coefficients,
    standard errors of the estimates, confidence intervals,
    predicted values, and residuals.
